videos.headline: Baylor strikes first with Sneed TD
videos.description: Initially called an incomplete pass, Baylor quarterback Charlie Brewer finds R.J. Sneed in the end zone for what is overturned to be a touchdown, giving Baylor the 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor strikes first with Sneed TD) 2019/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's botched trick play results in sack, fumble
videos.description: Baylor attempts a trick pass with wide receiver R.J. Sneed who is sacked by Tykee Smith, forcing a fumble that is recovered by Noah Guzman for West Virginia.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's botched trick play results in sack, fumble) 2019/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: West Virginia botches snap
videos.description: West Virginia botches the snap after driving to Baylor's 10-yard line, resulting in Baylor recovering the fumble.

videos.headline: West Virginia ties game on 83-yard TD pass
videos.description: West Virginia quarterback Austin Kendal finds George Campbell wide open for the 83-yard score, tying the game at 7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (West Virginia ties game on 83-yard TD pass) 2019/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor answers with a quick TD to retake lead
videos.description: Charlie Brewer finds Denzel Mims for the 21-yard touchdown as Baylor retakes the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor answers with a quick TD to retake lead) 2019/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: West Virginia bounces back with kickoff-return TD
videos.description: Jay Sedwick takes the kickoff 95 yards for the touchdown as West Virginia ties the game at 14-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (West Virginia bounces back with kickoff-return TD) 2019/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor fumbles punt, gives West Virginia great field position
videos.description: West Virginia's Kerry Martin Jr. recovers the fumbled punt, giving West Virginia great field position.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor fumbles punt, gives West Virginia great field position) 2019/10/31 ESHEET
